 />\n<br />\n悅耳 :1圈4鐵,6單 <br />\n美樂城seek keep: diy se535 vs2 <br />\n聲菲爾音頻商城 : diy K3003 <br />\n值得逛逛 : diy 535四單終極調音版動鐵版<br />\n線材 小凡/發燒銀線坊<br />\n<br />\n舊Post合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1pxY3M-1E0cpWfXhUhzqoo-Yiv2xIySlf8not4FcEcnQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1pxY3M-1E0cpWfXhUhzqoo-Yiv2xIySlf8not4FcEcnQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3igRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=3703a5c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1pxY3M-1E0cpWfXhUhzqoo-Yiv2xIySlf8not4FcEcnQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n開Post格式<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/ZQUicP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZQUicP&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3igRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=eeaee049\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ZQUicP</a><br />\n<br />\n使用器材列表<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1jwkKF3PE7SYRu5nbYMCdCOKkyKnwErYamydXRDUrdos/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1jwkKF3PE7SYRu5nbYMCdCOKkyKnwErYamydXRDUrdos%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3igRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=3143b529\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1jwkKF3PE7SYRu5nbYMCdCOKkyKnwErYamydXRDUrdos/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\f<br />\n#2 評價<br />\n________________________________________________________ <br />\n點解會係上面幾間鋪頭呢,就係根據EPC同高登會員既評論總結番黎 <br />\n評論: <br />\n對於悅耳 既 1圈4鐵,6單 / 夢想兔945 既 仿fitear 335 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n悅耳出左隻6單 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkepc.com/forum/viewthread.php?fid=124&amp;tid=2256623&amp;extra=page%3D1  \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2Fforum%2Fviewthread.php%3Ffid%3D124%26tid%3D2256623%26extra%3Dpage%253D1%20%20&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3igRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=800bf57b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkepc.com/forum/viewthread.php?fid=124&amp;tid=2256623&amp;extra=page%3D1  </a><br />\n對於悅耳 既 1圈4鐵,6單 / 美樂城seek keep原創 既 diy se535 vs2 / 聲菲爾音頻商城 既 仿K3003 / 值得逛逛 既 diy 535四單終極調音版動鐵版 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[玩耳系列]國產公模動圈耳機 <br />\n <a href=\"http://forum14.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=HW&amp;message=6151940&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum14.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DHW%26message%3D6151940%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse%20&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3igRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e66ddc9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum14.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=HW&amp;message=6151940&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False </a><br />\n________________________________________________________ <br />\n對於無畏定制既CM: <br />\n請教想淘CM耳機(永X還是無X好哩?) <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkepc.com/forum/viewthread.php?tid=2219847&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=2  \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2Fforum%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D2219847%26extra%3Dpage%253D1%26page%3D2%20%20&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3igRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=1d7a0b86\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkepc.com/forum/viewthread.php?tid=2219847&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=2  </a><br />\n<br />\n________________________________________________________ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\f<br />\n#3<br />\n伏List:<br />\n巴絲打們要小心! 市面上充斥住以動圈冒充動鐵o既&quot;DIY846&quot;產品<br />\n<br />\n例子:<br />\n <a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.7.hMylIu&amp;id=538300020915&amp;ns=1&amp;abbucket=12#detail  \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.taobao.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.7.hMylIu%26id%3D538300020915%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D12%23detail%20%20&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3igRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=65e38f19\" target=\"_blank\">https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.7.hMylIu&amp;id=538300020915&amp;ns=1&amp;abbucket=12#detail  </a><br />\n呢隻6單元各位巴打點睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸貼吧有人拆過呢D黎睇 <br />\n佢Hi Hi到直情連動鐵都唔比你，係膠片涂銀色顏料再包住個動圈 而且好似話咁多間都係同一個騙子開o既，所以問佢咩單元組合係冇意思  任佢嗡 <br />\n<br />\n我總結呢D假野o既常見特點係: <br />\n1. 5/6單DIY846 <br />\n2. 只有金屬紅色同銅色(非鏡面)，兩種色都係正版846冇o既，絕對唔會有透明你揀 <br />\n3. 清一色好評，極少評論有提負面野 <br />\n4. 通常會話提供一年，甚至三年保養 (因為佢好快就會閂鋪/比人封) <br />\n5. 間鋪只有極少種類商品 (因為佢好快就會閂鋪/比人封) <br />\n6. 提供15-30日無理由退貨 (因為佢好快就會閂鋪/比人封)<br />\n7. 你問佢單元型號/組合，佢會答22955+29689+30017'同級單元'之類 <br />\n8. 有會提供一條黑色耳機線(帶咪/不帶咪)比你買 <br />\n<br />\n你地自己考慮啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef：<br />\n <a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4757794747?share=9105 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F4757794747%3Fshare%3D9105%20&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3igRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f14e31d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4757794747?share=9105 </a><br />\n <a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4818363139?share=9105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F4818363139%3Fshare%3D9105&d=BV1dIdK0AL8otK5DimM3igRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4773fe08\" target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4818363139?share=9105</a>"},{"pid":"59aad334234567b810486ec44d6aa38b8eef1a7e","tid":479501,"uid":6460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"1001<br />\n今次手機開post唔小心開咗個去吹水台<br />\n請用返以下呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[url]淘寶耳機集中討論區(20)-窮撚耳機/DAP專用帖 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/479503/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/479503/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]"},{"pid":"557d0bfd0e7df122c7403ebb33b29bb0d717d832","tid":479501,"uid":108073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59aad334234567b810486ec44d6aa38b8eef1a7e","tid":479501,"uid":6460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"1001<br />\n今次手機開post唔小心開咗個去吹水台<br />\n請用返以下呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[url]淘寶耳機集中討論區(20)-窮撚耳機/DAP專用帖 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com